0.12.31.name: wordpress/tiny-table-of-contents-tinytoc
0.12.31.description: Plugin that enables you to create table of contents in your posts and pages. You can choose what it will parse, and what it will not parse. It's very simple to use from your editor so you do not have to manualy enter tags. Now it's nothing special, but later it will have much more features including some predefined styles and more styling control.
